text: Jan-Henrik Fredriksen (2 October 1956 – 8 March 2020) was a Norwegian politician. He was a member of the Progress Party (FRP). He served as a representative of Finnmark in the Storting from 2005 to 2017. Fredriksen was born in Kragerø, Telemark. He died on 8 March 2020, at the age of 63. ==References== ==Other websites== *Jan-Henrik Fredriksen profile Category:1956 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Norwegian politicians
